graphql.query:
query getTransactions {
  transactions(limit: 3, transferNextToken: "null", transferRequestNextToken: "null", filter: {}) {
    transferNextToken
    transferRequestNextToken
    transferHasMorePages
    transferRequestHasMorePages
    items {
      belongsTo
      createdAt
      amount
      behavior
      code
      currency
      description
      type
      requestState
      requestDetails {
        id
        name
        kashtag
        state
        amount
      }
      transactionDetails {
        remittanceAmount
        subType
        remittanceCurrency
        remittanceCountry
      }
      involved {
        id
        name
        kashtag
        transactionType
        destination
        destinationName
        destinationKashtag
        destinationCurrency
        destinationAmount
        service {
          reference
          company
          service
          billOwner
          dueDate
          payingService
          receipt
          referenceCode
        }
        card
      }
      kashtag
      card
      reversal
      fee
      favorite
    }
  }
}

body.raw:
{
    "source": {{idPaymentInstrument}},
    "currency": "{{currencyValue}}",
